(2, 1, '2014-04-13 19:59:45', '2014-04-13 19:59:45', '[et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_image="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/render.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="MainSectionFW"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_blurb admin_label="dmcSloganLogo" url_new_window="off" use_icon="off" icon_color="#f7323f" use_circle="off" circle_color="#f7323f" use_circle_border="off" circle_border_color="#f7323f" image="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/unnamed-1.png" icon_placement="top" animation="off" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="HandHubBg"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Emptyness" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]<div align="justify">\r\n<h2>This is Domocracy</h2>\r\n<p align="justify" style="color:black">Homes are getting populated with controls for lights, audio systems, thermostats, and more. We want to go one step beyond and make them interact with you, and learn from you. Domocracy’s Hub acts as a bridge between all your smart devices, our cloud service, and you. It communicates different devices and adds an extra layer of intelligence</p>\r\n</div>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_image="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/livingrom.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_image admin_label="MockupApp" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/combinedApps.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" module_class="MockupApp" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_text admin_label="Description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left" module_class="MockupAppDescription"]<p style="color: black; padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;" align="justify">Interact with your home using the smartphone application. Pair new devices, create custom scenes or attach actions to switches so you needn''t the application later.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_image="http://www.domocracytech.com.php54-3.dfw1-2.websitetestlink.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/unnamed-2.png" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="dmc affordable" title="DOMOCRACY IS AFFORDABLE" use_background_color="off" background_color="#ff314f" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="left" /][et_pb_text admin_label="affordable_description" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\nOther solutions force the user to depend on a specific smart technology, rising prices to a high and unnecessary level. Our system is designed to be 100% customizable and to adapt to future technologies at the time that uses resources already available at home (like the existing electrical wiring) to reduce costs. This allows us to provide the most advanced technology, at the most affordable price for a smarthome device, ever.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_image="http://www.domocracytech.com.php54-3.dfw1-2.websitetestlink.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/OpenSource_DomocracyWeb.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Emptyness" use_background_color="off" background_color="#ff314f" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Tittle" title="WE ARE OPEN SOURCE" use_background_color="off" background_color="#ff314f" background_layout="light" text_orientation="right" /][et_pb_text admin_label="description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="right"]\r\n<p style="color: black;">Domocracy is not a closed solution. Neither is it a restrictive, poorly-maintained API, solution. Domocracy is Open-Source for real. Yes, we provide a RESTful API for you to play with. But it doesn’t end there. You want more? We will Host the code on GitHub for you to download and modify as you please, as well as blueprints and CAD models for all hardware.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="SupportedDevicesHeader" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<h1>Supported Devices</h1>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image admin_label="SupportedDevicesLogos" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Supported_devices_logos_banner.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="off" /][et_pb_text admin_label="Description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\nSince day one, we will support Nest, Philips Hue, Insteon, X10, KODI (formerly XBMC), LG and samsung smartTVs and some wearables as Nike Fuel and LG’s LifeBand. However, adding devices to our list of compatibility is an ongoing effort. Above we have given a list of devices we currently plan to integrate, but do not hesitate to ask for your favorite technology!\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#f7323f" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="GreetingsHeader" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<h1>Greetings</h1>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="GreetingsLogos" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="https://www.openfuture.org/"><img style="display: inline-block;" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/openfuure.png" alt="openfuure" width="170" height="40" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="www.paypal.com"><img style="display: inline-block;" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/paypal.png" alt="paypal" width="145" height="36" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="http://bolt.eu.com/en/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-319" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/bolt.png" alt="bolt" width="101" height="51" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="https://developers.google.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-320" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/google.png" alt="google" width="141" height="32" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="http://aws.amazon.com/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-318" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/amazon.png" alt="amazon" width="177" height="52" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#f7323f" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="ContactSection"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="2_3"][et_pb_text admin_label="Contact" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<h3>Contact</h3>\r\n<ul class="list-unstyled">\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">Support:</span> <a href="mailto:support@domocracytect.com">support@domocracytech.com</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;">PR:</span> <a href="mailto:press@domocracytech.com">press@domocracytech.com</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_3"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'HOME', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2015-02-05 15:11:58', '2015-02-05 15:11:58', '', 0, 'http://www.domocracy.es.php53-7.dfw1-2.websitetestlink.com/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
