his technology. So we made smart homes easy.</p><p>Adding a new device is as simple as pluging it in and activate There is no installation required, and no complex setup to do. Just download our app and start controlling your home appliances today.</p>[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="on" specialty="off"][et_pb_fullwidth_header admin_label="Fullwidth Header" /][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="It''s low cost" title="It''s low cost" use_background_color="on" background_color="#ffffff" background_layout="light" text_orientation="center"]<p>Let me show you how inexpensive it is.</p><p>All devices in the house are connected together through the  house’s existing wiring. And the network connects to the internet through our gateway. This reduces the overall complexity of the system. Your devices no longer need to have wi-fi or bluetooth, hence diminishing its cost.</p>[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_image admin_label="Image" src="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/diagrama-plc.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" /][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_slider admin_label="Slider" show_arrows="on" show_pagination="on" auto="on" parallax="off" auto_speed="5000"][et_pb_slide background_image="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/belerofonte.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark"]<p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide background_image="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/belerofonte-2.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" alignment="center" background_layout="dark" /][et_pb_slide background_image="http://www.domocracy.es/wp-co