pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_image="http://www.domocracytech.com.php54-3.dfw1-2.websitetestlink.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/OpenSource_DomocracyWeb.jpg" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Emptyness" use_background_color="off" background_color="#ff314f" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="center" /][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2"][et_pb_cta admin_label="Tittle" title="WE ARE OPEN SOURCE" use_background_color="off" background_color="#ff314f" background_layout="light" text_orientation="right" /][et_pb_text admin_label="description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="right"]\r\n<p style="color: black;">Domocracy is not a closed solution. Neither is it a restrictive, poorly-maintained API, solution. Domocracy is Open-Source for real. Yes, we provide a RESTful API for you to play with. But it doesn’t end there. You want more? We will Host the code on GitHub for you to download and modify as you please, as well as blueprints and CAD models for all hardware.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="SupportedDevicesHeader" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<h1>Supported Devices</h1>\r\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_image admin_label="SupportedDevicesLogos" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Supported_devices_logos_banner.png" show_in_lightbox="off" url_new_window="off" animation="left" /][et_pb_text admin_label="Description" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n\r\nSince day one, we will support Nest, Philips Hue, Insteon, X10, KODI (formerly XBMC), LG and samsung smartTVs and some wearables as Nike Fuel and LG’s LifeBand. However, adding devices to our list of compatibility is an ongoing effort. Above we have given a list of devices we currently plan to integrate, but do not hesitate to ask for your favorite technology!\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#f7323f" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="GreetingsHeader" background_layout="dark" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<h1>Greetings</h1>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fullwidth="off" specialty="off" background_color="#ffffff" inner_shadow="off" parallax="off" parallax_method="css" module_class="PaddingB0T20"][et_pb_row][et_pb_column type="4_4"][et_pb_text admin_label="GreetingsLogos" background_layout="light" text_orientation="left"]\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="https://www.openfuture.org/"><img style="display: inline-block;" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/openfuure.png" alt="openfuure" width="170" height="40" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="www.paypal.com"><img style="display: inline-block;" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/paypal.png" alt="paypal" width="145" height="36" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="http://bolt.eu.com/en/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-319" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/bolt.png" alt="bolt" width="101" height="51" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="GreetingImageContainer"><a href="https://developers.google.com"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-320" src="http://www.domocracytech.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/google.png" alt="google" width="141" height="32" /></a></div>\r\n<div class="